  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Assemble your team of heroes, unlock synergy buffs, and craft rare artifacts. Choose powerful combat perks to enhance your builds, then challenge other players and conquer new lands!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2886470/extras/47f18e29738b0f5d2393b55c511ee5d8.poster.avif?t=1737986742\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2886470/extras/47f18e29738b0f5d2393b55c511ee5d8.webm?t=1737986742\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2886470/extras/47f18e29738b0f5d2393b55c511ee5d8.mp4?t=1737986742\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Team Building</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Valefor, you fight with a team equipped with powerful items. The heroes you choose matter, as each has unique abilities and belongs to a specific class and race. The smarter you equip and position your heroes, the better your chances of victory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2886470/extras/1b5ec8a95c9bb45309ead0aa9d0fad8c.poster.avif?t=1737986742\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2886470/extras/1b5ec8a95c9bb45309ead0aa9d0fad8c.webm?t=1737986742\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2886470/extras/1b5ec8a95c9bb45309ead0aa9d0fad8c.mp4?t=1737986742\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Summon and Craft</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect fragments from loot or buy them in the shop, and use them to summon units and craft equipment. Combine them to create even stronger heroes and artifacts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2886470/extras/f8d425ca7aeb9a1eeaac73d8b9c4f379.poster.avif?t=1737986742\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2886470/extras/f8d425ca7aeb9a1eeaac73d8b9c4f379.webm?t=1737986742\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2886470/extras/f8d425ca7aeb9a1eeaac73d8b9c4f379.mp4?t=1737986742\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Ranked PVP</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight against real party builds, made by real players, in our  PVP Arena. Ascend the ranks in true roguelike fashion, with a new team built from scratch every run. Analyze the strategy used by your opponents, press advantages and try to counter them. Take your time experimenting with the vast array of heroes, perks and items at your disposal because - with Asynchronous PVP - there is no turn timer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2886470/extras/5935b04d0b72ff26c35c126d1bafd5eb.poster.avif?t=1737986742\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2886470/extras/5935b04d0b72ff26c35c126d1bafd5eb.webm?t=1737986742\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2886470/extras/5935b04d0b72ff26c35c126d1bafd5eb.mp4?t=1737986742\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Solo Campaign</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Valefor is a Roguelite Strategy Auto-Battle RPG that is lightweight enough for portable play, and deep enough for tactical gameplay.  Step into a rich dark fantasy world and follow the fragmented story in a single player campaign building your Kingdom along the way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2886470/extras/5c5520738d87d9ca36cc30b9e779b7f6.poster.avif?t=1737986742\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2886470/extras/5c5520738d87d9ca36cc30b9e779b7f6.webm?t=1737986742\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2886470/extras/5c5520738d87d9ca36cc30b9e779b7f6.mp4?t=1737986742\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Expand your Kingdom</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every class and faction in the game has its own unique Building that can be constructed and upgraded to unlock powerful synergy buffs, give heroes class specific starting equipment and can even increase max party sizes.  Defeat the dungeons that have taken hold of the land to unlock more space to grow your Kingdom.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2886470/extras/c026e540a509b073e2c1acf5d10cf5ca.poster.avif?t=1737986742\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2886470/extras/c026e540a509b073e2c1acf5d10cf5ca.webm?t=1737986742\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2886470/extras/c026e540a509b073e2c1acf5d10cf5ca.mp4?t=1737986742\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Epic Soundtrack and Lore</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >On top of Valefor’s sleek visuals- we’ve also included a soundtrack and story to match.  Whether it’s an epic score, a mournful ambience, or an action-packed battle scene- our music and lore seek to immerse you in our world and enhance your gaming experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2886470/extras/6aa51696f1adf7d21c27456f3025f63b.poster.avif?t=1737986742\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2886470/extras/6aa51696f1adf7d21c27456f3025f63b.webm?t=1737986742\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2886470/extras/6aa51696f1adf7d21c27456f3025f63b.mp4?t=1737986742\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Active Development</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Here at Valefor, we are constantly working to make this game the best we can- and we can’t do that without you. Have ideas, critiques, bug reports or just want to chat?  Check out our Discord - we are incredibly active there. You can also visit our site, join our newsletter for development updates- or check out our many social accounts.    We appreciate your support!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Assemble your team of heroes, unlock synergy buffs, and craft rare artifacts. Choose powerful combat perks to enhance your builds, then challenge other players and conquer new lands!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2886470/extras/47f18e29738b0f5d2393b55c511ee5d8.poster.avif?t=1737986742\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2886470/extras/47f18e29738b0f5d2393b55c511ee5d8.webm?t=1737986742\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2886470/extras/47f18e29738b0f5d2393b55c511ee5d8.mp4?t=1737986742\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Team Building</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Valefor, you fight with a team equipped with powerful items. The heroes you choose matter, as each has unique abilities and belongs to a specific class and race. The smarter you equip and position your heroes, the better your chances of victory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2886470/extras/1b5ec8a95c9bb45309ead0aa9d0fad8c.poster.avif?t=1737986742\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2886470/extras/1b5ec8a95c9bb45309ead0aa9d0fad8c.webm?t=1737986742\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2886470/extras/1b5ec8a95c9bb45309ead0aa9d0fad8c.mp4?t=1737986742\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Summon and Craft</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect fragments from loot or buy them in the shop, and use them to summon units and craft equipment. Combine them to create even stronger heroes and artifacts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2886470/extras/f8d425ca7aeb9a1eeaac73d8b9c4f379.poster.avif?t=1737986742\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2886470/extras/f8d425ca7aeb9a1eeaac73d8b9c4f379.webm?t=1737986742\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2886470/extras/f8d425ca7aeb9a1eeaac73d8b9c4f379.mp4?t=1737986742\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Ranked PVP</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight against real party builds, made by real players, in our  PVP Arena. Ascend the ranks in true roguelike fashion, with a new team built from scratch every run. Analyze the strategy used by your opponents, press advantages and try to counter them. Take your time experimenting with the vast array of heroes, perks and items at your disposal because - with Asynchronous PVP - there is no turn timer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2886470/extras/5935b04d0b72ff26c35c126d1bafd5eb.poster.avif?t=1737986742\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2886470/extras/5935b04d0b72ff26c35c126d1bafd5eb.webm?t=1737986742\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2886470/extras/5935b04d0b72ff26c35c126d1bafd5eb.mp4?t=1737986742\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Solo Campaign</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Valefor is a Roguelite Strategy Auto-Battle RPG that is lightweight enough for portable play, and deep enough for tactical gameplay.  Step into a rich dark fantasy world and follow the fragmented story in a single player campaign building your Kingdom along the way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2886470/extras/5c5520738d87d9ca36cc30b9e779b7f6.poster.avif?t=1737986742\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2886470/extras/5c5520738d87d9ca36cc30b9e779b7f6.webm?t=1737986742\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2886470/extras/5c5520738d87d9ca36cc30b9e779b7f6.mp4?t=1737986742\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Expand your Kingdom</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every class and faction in the game has its own unique Building that can be constructed and upgraded to unlock powerful synergy buffs, give heroes class specific starting equipment and can even increase max party sizes.  Defeat the dungeons that have taken hold of the land to unlock more space to grow your Kingdom.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2886470/extras/c026e540a509b073e2c1acf5d10cf5ca.poster.avif?t=1737986742\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2886470/extras/c026e540a509b073e2c1acf5d10cf5ca.webm?t=1737986742\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2886470/extras/c026e540a509b073e2c1acf5d10cf5ca.mp4?t=1737986742\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Epic Soundtrack and Lore</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >On top of Valefor’s sleek visuals- we’ve also included a soundtrack and story to match.  Whether it’s an epic score, a mournful ambience, or an action-packed battle scene- our music and lore seek to immerse you in our world and enhance your gaming experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2886470/extras/6aa51696f1adf7d21c27456f3025f63b.poster.avif?t=1737986742\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2886470/extras/6aa51696f1adf7d21c27456f3025f63b.webm?t=1737986742\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2886470/extras/6aa51696f1adf7d21c27456f3025f63b.mp4?t=1737986742\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Active Development</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Here at Valefor, we are constantly working to make this game the best we can- and we can’t do that without you. Have ideas, critiques, bug reports or just want to chat?  Check out our Discord - we are incredibly active there. You can also visit our site, join our newsletter for development updates- or check out our many social accounts.    We appreciate your support!</p>",
